data.description: Welcome to this charming brick home located in the established neighborhood of Dorsett Woods. This beautiful residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and plenty of space to start creating new memories! The entire main level has hardwoods through out including the primary bedroom. The primary bedroom is HUGE and on the main level. The gourmet kitchen offers ample counterspace and stainless steel appliances. You'll love whipping up meals on your gas stove and this kitchen also offers a space for a separate desk area or to keep all your mail organized! One of the highlights of this home is the NEW finished basement, which offers new luxury vinyl plank flooring in both rooms. Don't miss this opportunity to make this brick home your own!
